<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA61">
<l>niṉṟatōr pāta nilamputaippa nīṇṭatōḷ</l>
<l>ceṉṟaḷanta teṉpar ticaiyellā – maṉṟu</l>
<l>karumāṇi yāyiranta kaḷvaṉē yuṉṉaip</l>
<l>piramāṇit tārpeṟṟa pēṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One foot stood, the arms lengthened so as to cover the ground,</l>
<l>in going it measured all the directions, they say, o robber</l>
<l>who that day begged as an embryo-dwarf , [o you who is] the goal obtained</l>
<l>by those who put [their] trust in you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
